  "detailed_description": "Enjoy a fresh new RPG adventure. As a courier, your next delivery awaits, and this time it's a special delivery to someone who is no-where to be found.<br>As you explore, you encounter memorable people, rich story telling, evil bosses and a lot of fun. But be careful someone has an eye on the package. Can you deliver it on time?<br>It's up to you to reach your next destination to find out about the whereabouts of the owner and the mysterious contents of the package.<br><br>Futures:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 200 side quests<br></li><li>6000 random events<br></li><li>Turn based Battles<br></li><li>Summons<br></li><li>Mini-games (with other online players)<br></li><li>Rich story telling</li></ul><br>Optional<br>Adult content dlc<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888120/extras/d1223ace7d142f35974f14aae3071bb0.webp?t=1756113478\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888120/extras/d1223ace7d142f35974f14aae3071bb0.poster.avif?t=1756113478\" class=\"bb_img\" width=300 height=600 /></picture></span>",
